    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GORECORE is a fast paced atmospheric movement shooter inspired by ULTRAKILL, BLAME!, and Lorn's Lure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164260/extras/c49d8f60a12faa0535bdf6701d0c3abf.poster.avif?t=1754419781\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164260/extras/c49d8f60a12faa0535bdf6701d0c3abf.webm?t=1754419781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164260/extras/c49d8f60a12faa0535bdf6701d0c3abf.mp4?t=1754419781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rip through the defenses of an uncontrollable <strong>megastructure</strong>, avenge your fallen people, and destroy the <strong>core</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164260/extras/74b95236ea1602b1e3df7e42a7320f5e.poster.avif?t=1754419781\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164260/extras/74b95236ea1602b1e3df7e42a7320f5e.webm?t=1754419781\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164260/extras/74b95236ea1602b1e3df7e42a7320f5e.mp4?t=1754419781\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through the atmospheric story mode/Campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find out the limits of your skill in the endless mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seek out hidden weapons, bosses and levels for an extra challenge</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Containing many different weapon combinations and synergies, GORECORE offers a challenging experience with a high skill ceiling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
